      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Mayhem</b>\n</p><p><b>Mayhem</b>, (Mayhem NNUE)<br />\nan <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant  <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> by <a href=\"/Toni_Helminen\" title=\"Toni Helminen\">Toni Helminen</a>, written in <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++17</a>, licensed under the <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GPL v3.0</a>.\nMayham was created by porting the author's former engine <a href=\"/Sapeli\" title=\"Sapeli\">Sapeli</a>, written in plain <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a>, to C++17,\nutilizing <a href=\"/Stockfish_NNUE\" title=\"Stockfish NNUE\">Stockfish's NNUE</a> evaluation via <a href=\"/Daniel_Shawul\" title=\"Daniel Shawul\">Daniel Shawul's</a> <a href=\"/Scorpio#ScorpioNNUE\" title=\"Scorpio\">Scorpio NNUE</a> <a href=\"/Scorpio#Bitbases\" title=\"Scorpio\">egbbdll</a> probing library \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mayhem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/BBC\" title=\"BBC\">BBC</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/CFish\" title=\"CFish\">CFish</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Sapeli\" title=\"Sapeli\">Sapeli</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Scorpio#ScorpioNNUE\" title=\"Scorpio\">Scorpio NNUE</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Stockfish_NNUE\" title=\"Stockfish NNUE\">Stockfish NNUE</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mayhem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75500\">Mayhem NNUE - New NN engine</a> by <a href=\"/Toni_Helminen\" title=\"Toni Helminen\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 22, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=77503&amp;start=55\">Re: will Tcec allow Stockfish with a Leela net to play?</a> by <a href=\"/Connor_McMonigle\" title=\"Connor McMonigle\">Connor McMonigle</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 17, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mayhem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Engine\">Chess Engine</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mayhem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Engine\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/SamuraiDangyo/mayhem\">GitHub - SamuraiDangyo/mayhem: Linux UCI Chess960 engine</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mayhem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.chessvariants.com/diffsetup.dir/mayhem.html\">Mayhem Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/mayhem\">mayhem - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mayhem\">Mayhem from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mayhem_(comics)\">Mayhem (comics) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mayhem!_(comics)\">Mayhem! (comics) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mayhem_(crime)\">Mayhem (crime) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mayhem_(band)\">Mayhem</a> - <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daemon_(Mayhem_album)\">Aeon Daemonium</a> (2019), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/DSYXjJvDBQs?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mayhem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75482\">BBC 1.3 + Stockfish NNUE released!</a> by <a href=\"/Maksim_Korzh\" title=\"Maksim Korzh\">Maksim Korzh</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 21, 2020</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75500\">Mayhem NNUE - New NN engine</a> by <a href=\"/Toni_Helminen\" title=\"Toni Helminen\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 22, 2020</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301044013\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor vis